"""
Yillik 1700 Combiner — CustomTkinter GUI app

Runs BOTH master pipelines and concatenates their outputs into ONE Excel file.

Pipeline A (test.xlsx-style flow): 7 sub-pipelines that produce the
  25-column FINAL_COLS_A schema (with ns_name).

Pipeline B (test2.xlsx-style flow): 4 master pipelines that produce the
  24-column FINAL_COLS_B schema.

Both result frames are aligned to the union of columns and stacked into
one final Excel file with a single sheet.

Inputs (chosen in the GUI):
  - 1-fx shakli_Yillik_1700.csv          + katalog for fx.xlsx
  - 1- nnt shakli_Yillik_1700.csv        + katalog for nnt.xlsx
  - 1-notijorat shakli_Yillik_1700.csv
  - 1-invest (asosiy) shakli_Yillik_1700.csv
  - 1 korxona shakli_Yillik.csv

Output:
  - User-chosen .xlsx file (default: all_combined_final.xlsx)
"""

